import styled from "styled-components"

const Logo = () => {
    const url = "https://ortex-static-files.s3.amazonaws.com/static/public/images/ortex_logo_v-white.svg"
    return <LogoImg alt="logo" src={url} />
}

export default Logo

const LogoImg = styled.img`
    width: 2em
`
